Tyrael looked at Spike and Talon. He hadn't yet met Spike, formally at 
least. He pushed down his anger and took a deep breath. Even though he 
did not truly breathe, the techno-organic arrangement of his body made 
this motion relaxing.

Tyrael: You must be one of our new warriors. I am Major Tyrael. Please 
tell me about you. Talon, can you install auto-defenses on the base? 
You are free to go to CR right after that. I want this to get done 
with as soon as possible. And where in the name of Gamma is Shadow 
Star?

He transformed and took Burrock's remain to a DNA containment capsule 
inside the ship. It could use later...
